#: ../../G/green-machine.rst:9
msgid ""
"A computer or peripheral device that has been designed and built to military"
" specifications for field equipment (that is, to withstand mechanical shock,"
" extremes of temperature and humidity, and so forth). Comes from the olive-"
"drab ‘uniform’ paint used for military equipment."
msgstr ""
"野外機器の軍用仕様(すなわち、機械的衝撃、極端な温度や湿度などに耐える)に合わせて設計・製造されたコンピュータまたは周辺機器。軍用機器に使われるオリーブドラブの‘制服’塗装に由来する。"
